{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_06_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 街中すっかりクリスマス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "――という訳で～\n{user}さんにも協力してほしいんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡSo‚ um…\nI want {user} to help me too~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "明後日のクリスマスライブで、琴乃の誕生日を\nサプライズでお祝いか。いいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're sayting celebrating Kotono's birthday with a surprise\nat the Christmas live the day after tomorrow. That'd be great!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "でしょ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4536730766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達が暗躍していることは\n琴乃に気付かれないよう、俺も注意するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To make sure Kotono doesn't notice what we're keeping from her‚\nI'll be careful too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "よろしく！\nでも暗躍って言い方はちょっと引っかかるな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks!\nBut‚ you know‚ the way you put it‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達が悪いことを企んでるみたいじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it sounds like Mei and everyone scheming something bad‚ doesn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達はいいことするんだから！\n琴乃ちゃんのサンタさんになるんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're doing a good thing‚ you know!\nWe're going to be Santa for Kotono-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、悪かった\nもし俺で良かったら協力するよ。なんでも言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right‚ my bad.\nIf it's okay with me‚ I'll help. Just tell me what to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも？　本当に！？　{user}さん\nなんでもしてくれるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anything? Really!? {user}-san?\nYou'll do anything for me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　……ああ、もちろんだ。任せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?… Uh‚ yeah‚ of course. Leave it to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "なら、もっと派手なステージにしたいな\n曲の最中におっきなツリーがニョキっと生えたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ I want to make the stage even more spectacular.\nLike having a big Christmas tree popping up during the song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "本物のトナカイさんがばーって出てきて\n芽衣達と一緒に踊るとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or a real reindeer coming out\nand dancing with Mei and everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さんは、サンタの格好して\nなんか高そうな車でステージに乗りつけてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ and {user}-san can dress up as Santa\nand arrive on with a fancy-looking car…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "それでメリークリスマス！　ハッピーバースデー！\nって、琴乃ちゃんに花束を渡すの。いいでしょ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ \"Merry Christmas! Happy Birthday!\"\nAnd give a bouquet to Kotono-chan. Isn't that great?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あの……予算的に現実的なラインを\n考慮していただけると、大変助かります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… If you could consider a more realistic budget…\nIt would be highly helpful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "そっか～、残念\nじゃ、お金がかからないことをお願いするね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I see. That's a shame.\nWell then‚ I'll ask for something that doesn't cost money.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、それなら大丈夫だ。全力で協力するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's fine then. I'll help with giving it my all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、早速お願い。行こうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great! Let's get started right away. Lets go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　今から？　どこに行くんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Right now? Where are we going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、早く早く～！　時間がないんだから～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ hurry! We don't have much time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ、スケジュールを確認しないと……\nって、そんなに引っ張らないでくれ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ let me check a schedule…\nDon't pull me like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.666666700002,
          "startTime": 124.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmastokyo",
      "startTime": 123.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmastokyo",
      "startTime": 123.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "せかいに～\nうたごえをひびかそ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this world~\nLet's make our voices travel~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmastokyo",
      "startTime": 131.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmastokyo",
      "startTime": 135.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "わーっ！　街中すっかりクリスマスだよ～\nほら、{user}さん、キレイ！　見て！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! The whole town is in full Christmas mode~\nLook‚ {user}-san‚ it's beautiful! Look!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmastokyo",
      "startTime": 139.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、そんなにはしゃいでると危ないぞ\nせっかく買った材料を落としたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ it's dangerous to get so excited like that.\nIf you drop the ingredients we just bought…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmastokyo",
      "startTime": 149.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "ケーキが作れなくなっちゃうよね。ごめんね～\nえへへ……芽衣、ついワクワクしちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won't be able to make the cake. Sorry~\nHehe… Mei got too excited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmastokyo",
      "startTime": 154.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ところで芽衣はケーキ、ちゃんと作れるのか？\n俺は作ったことないんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Mei‚ can you actually make the cake?\nI've never made one before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "うん、遙子ちゃんに教えてもらったから大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I learned from Haruko-chan‚ so it's going to be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmastokyo",
      "startTime": 165.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
